description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has opened within the Endoscopy department we are looking for a dynamic keen team player to join their booking team, you will be part of an extremely busy department within day surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are energetic, methodical, computer literate, proactive, able to cope with new challenging priorities and preferably with some NHS experience then we would like to hear from you . Are you an enthusiastic administrator with the ability to work as part of a team? If so, we would love to hear from you&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To be successful in this role:&lt;br /&gt;- You will have excellent written and communication skills&lt;br /&gt;- You will have a good telephone manner&lt;br /&gt;- You will have sound organisational skills&lt;br /&gt;- You will be able to work both in a team environment and autonomously&lt;br /&gt;- You will be expected to input data across trust applications, patient records system and/or database system and therefore excellent data entry skills are required&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent career development opportunity for a self-motivated and enthusiastic individual who wishes to pursue a career within the NHS.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time position, 37.5 hours per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lisa Bowyer Endoscopy Booking Coordinator lisa.bowyer@ydh.nhs.uk 01935 383062&lt;/p&gt;
